) ƒë·ªëi chi·∫øu gi·ªØa m·ªôt object ban ƒë·∫ßu\r\n// v·ªõi m·ªôt object ƒë√≠ch ƒë·∫øn c√≥ gi√° tr·ªã value g·∫•p hai l·∫ßn\r\n\r\nfunction doubleOf(theObject) {\r\n   var anotherObject = { value: theObject.value * 2 };\r\n   return anotherObject;\r\n}\r\n\r\nvar just = { value: 1 };\r\nvar anotherJust = doubleOf(just);\r\n\r\nconsole.log(just);   // { value: 1 }\r\nconsole.log(anotherJust);   // { value: 2 }\r\n</pre><p>V√† nh∆∞ ƒë√£ n√≥i, trong code v√≠ d·ª• ·ªü tr√™n, ch√∫ng ta ƒë√£ kh√¥ng th·ª±c hi·ªán thao t√°c n√†o t√°c ƒë·ªông l√™n&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">just</code>&nbsp;ƒë·ªÉ t·∫°o ra thay ƒë·ªïi v·ªÅ m·∫∑t n·ªôi dung c·ªßa&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">just</code>. C√°c&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">h√†m</code>&nbsp;ho√†n to√†n kh√¥ng quan t√¢m t·ªõi c√¢u h·ªèi&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">Vi·ªác c·∫ßn l√†m l√† g√¨?</code>; V√† c≈©ng kh√¥ng quan t√¢m t·ªõi c√°c y·∫øu t·ªë c·ªßa m√¥i tr∆∞·ªùng b√™n ngo√†i ph·∫ßn ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a h√†m.</p><p>Khi ch√∫ng ta s·ª≠ d·ª•ng h√†m&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">doubleOf</code>&nbsp;v√† cung c·∫•p m·ªôt object&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">just</code>&nbsp;b·∫•t k·ª≥ v√†o v·ªã tr√≠ c·ªßa tham s·ªë&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">theObject</code>, th√¨ logic ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a b·ªüi&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">doubleOf</code>&nbsp;s·∫Ω ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ªùng cho ch√∫ng ta t√¨m ƒë·∫øn m·ªôt object kh√°c&nbsp;<code style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: inherit;\">anotherJust</code>. Theo c√°ch n√≥i c·ªßa c√°c b·∫°n y√™u th√≠ch m√¥n to√°n th√¨ ƒë√≥ l√† m·ªôt √°nh x·∫° t·ª´ mi·ªÅn gi√° tr·ªã n√†y sang m·ªôt mi·ªÅn gi√° tr·ªã kh√°c. M·∫•y t·ª´&nbsp;<code style=\"