a k·ªπ thu·∫≠t: JDK l√† m·ªôt tri·ªÉn khai c·ªßa ƒë·∫∑c t·∫£ n·ªÅn t·∫£ng Java, bao g·ªìm c√°c tr√¨nh bi√™n d·ªãch v√† th∆∞ vi·ªán l·ªõp.</li><li>ƒê·ªãnh nghƒ©a h√†ng ng√†y: JDK l√† g√≥i ph·∫ßn m·ªÅm b·∫°n t·∫£i xu·ªëng ƒë·ªÉ t·∫°o c√°c ·ª©ng d·ª•ng d·ª±a tr√™n Java.</li></ul><p>Ngu·ªìn tham kh·∫£o:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.javaworld.com/article/3272244/what-is-the-jvm-introducing-the-java-virtual-machine.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: initial; color: rgb(43, 109, 173);\">https://www.javaworld.com/article/3272244/what-is-the-jvm-introducing-the-java-virtual-machine.html</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.javaworld.com/article/3296360/what-is-the-jdk-introduction-to-the-java-development-kit.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: initial; color: rgb(43, 109, 173);\">https://www.javaworld.com/article/3296360/what-is-the-jdk-introduction-to-the-java-development-kit.html</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.javaworld.com/article/3304858/what-is-the-jre-introduction-to-the-java-runtime-environment.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: initial; color: rgb(43, 109, 173);\">https://www.javaworld.com/article/3304858/what-is-the-jre-introduction-to-the-java-runtime-environment.html</a></p>',1,'2022-05-13 08:04:50','2022-05-13 08:04:50',NULL),(24,5,'Di·ªÖn gi·∫£i chi ti·∫øt v·ªÅ OOP trong Java','Dien_giai_chi_tiet_ve_OOP_trong_Java','','/images/posts/5/oop-la-gi_4132022T15742.jpg','<h2><strong>1. L·∫≠p tr√¨nh h∆∞·ªõng ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng (Oriented Object Programming - OOP) l√† g√¨?</strong></h2><ul><li>L·∫≠p tr√¨nh h∆∞·ªõng ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng l√† m·ªôt m√¥ h√¨nh l·∫≠p tr√¨nh m√°y t√≠nh d·ª±a tr√™n kh√°i ni·ªám l·ªõp v√† ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng.</li><li>L·∫•y ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng l√†m n·ªÅn t·∫£ng ƒë·ªÉ x√¢y d·ª±ng gi·∫£i thu·∫≠t, x√¢y d·ª±ng ch∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh v√† th·ª±c hi·ªán x·ª≠ l√Ω d·ªØ li·ªáu v·ªõi ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng ƒë√£ ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a ƒë√≥.</li><li>Nh·∫±m t·ªëi ∆∞u h√≥a vi·ªác qu·∫£n l√Ω m√£ ngu·ªìn (source code), t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng m√£ ngu·ªìn, t√≥m g·ªçn c√°c th·ªß t·ª•c ƒë√£ bi·∫øt tr∆∞·ªõc t√≠nh ch·∫•t th√¥ng qua vi·ªác s·ª≠ d·ª•ng ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng.</li><li>M·ªôt ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a l√† m·ªôt tr∆∞·ªùng d·ªØ li·ªáu c√≥ c√°c thu·ªôc t√≠nh v√† c√°c h√†nh ƒë·ªông c·ªßa ri√™ng n√≥:</li><li><em>V√≠ d·ª• 1</em></li></ul><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">// 1 v√≠ d·ª• ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n v·ªÅ ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a l·ªõp ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng *ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh b·∫≠c 2* ax^2 + bx + c = 0 trong java:\r\npublic class PTB2 {\r\n    // Khai b√°o c√°c thu·ªôc t√≠nh c·ªßa m·ªôt ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh b·∫≠c 2 g·ªìm c√°c h·ªá s·ªë th·ª±c a, b, c\r\n    private double a, b, c;\r\n    \r\n    // Khai b√°o c√°c ph∆∞∆°ng th·ª©c hay h√†nh ƒë·ªông c√≥ th·ªÉ l√†m c·ªßa l·ªõp ƒë·ªëi t∆∞·ª£ng n√†y\r\n    // T√≠nh delta\r\n    public double delta() {\r\n        return b * b - 4 * a * c;\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    // T√¨m nghi·ªám trong t·∫≠p s·ªë th·ª±c R v√† in ra m√†n h√¨nh\r\n    public void timNo(){\r\n        // T√≠nh v√† l∆∞u gi√° tr·ªã delta v√†o m·ªôt bi·∫øn\r\n        double dt = delta();\r\n        \r\n        // X√©t ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán ( bao g·ªìm delta v√† h·ªá s·ªë a ) v√† ti·∫øn h√†nh t√¨m nghi·ªám\r\n        if(a == 0){\r\n            /* Ch√∫ng ta ch·ªâ x√©t nh·∫≠p v√†o m·ªôt ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh b·∫≠c 2 v√† gi·∫£i nghi·ªám ch·∫≥ng h·∫°n,\r\n            n√™n khi ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng nh·∫≠p a = 0 ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω hi·ªÉn th·ªã th√¥ng b√°o nh∆∞ sau. ^^*/\r\n            System.out.println(\"- Ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh b·∫≠c 2 ph·∫£i c√≥ h·ªá s·ªë a kh√°c 0.\");\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            if(dt &lt; 0)\r\n                 System.out.println(\"- Ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh v√¥ nghi·ªám.\");\r\n             else if(dt == 0){\r\n                 System.out.printf(\"- Ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh c√≥ nghi·ªám k√©p x1 = x2 = %.3f\\n\", -b / 2 * a);\r\n             }\r\n             else{\r\n                 System.out.println(\"- Ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh c√≥ 2 nghi·ªám ph√¢n bi·ªát:\");\r\n                 System.out.printf(\"\\tx1 = %.3f\\n\", (-b + sqrt(dt)) / 2 * a);\r\